name: UnofficialOMGUbuntu
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: This puts the OMG! Ubuntu! site in your flash briefing. Please note that this is not official and is not endorsed by OMG! Ubuntu!. Go to omgubuntu.co.uk for the source of the news.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
